name: My Eyes Hurt
description:
There's so much noise, so much hate and anger in this world. I wish someone could tape its mouth. But what about the image? Painted by social media, with bright happy colours and background music, as if all is good and pretty. It is not. It's a facade in front of everything that is wrong. Everything is just glorified noise to cover up the real issues. Its so damn colourful and sweet, my eyes hurt!

by sagarkapoor29
